{"tid":335750,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"泊車疑問","createTime":"2017-07-25T23:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T05:43:44.000Z","uid":60464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1fa6270fa2bb196e359afa90ab89bd364769486","tid":335750,"uid":60464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:42:47.000Z","msg":"點解大部分泊車都係要倒車泊入去？<br />\n車頭泊入去倒車抽返出黎唔係應該易過倒車泊入去咩？"},{"pid":"043fc27c8ece0b0d841d1742b69d774347db4c95","tid":335750,"uid":131041,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:44:14.000Z","msg":"個個都泊車 唔通個個都泊車咩"},{"pid":"5078fdccdc61771bdf258d3ae87c2a75ef10d4c6","tid":335750,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:46:25.000Z","msg":"香港位窄，頭入係唔夠位扭"},{"pid":"3c8990f4512bcb138dbd21a61d70eff8e40bf189","tid":335750,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解大部分泊車都係要倒車泊入去？<br />\n車頭泊入去倒車抽返出黎唔係應該易過倒車泊入去咩？</blockquote><br />\n如果你係外國<br />\n你會見到多數人用頭就咁扭入去<br />\n因為人地國家地大"},{"pid":"851cf73c389db1b93ac12a284f1290d270cd3102","tid":335750,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:22:30.000Z","msg":"主要係後泊有後泊鏡 預位準好多"},{"pid":"001c6c93c6c880a4ba44d71be4c4c113c695a03b","tid":335750,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港位窄，頭入係唔夠位扭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新牌仔表示<br />\n<br />\n頭入唔知幾時扭<br />\n<br />\n早驚hi到右邊<br />\n<br />\n痴驚hi到後面"},{"pid":"a80d788da975ecd8f70ae20f67ef829f86f3c77e","tid":335750,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:37:07.000Z","msg":"車頭入 架車唔會好直  除非直路到尾去泊車"},{"pid":"a3acb25f7fc854a66d70168914927091808caaa5","tid":335750,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"尾入再開車果下安全d我覺得"},{"pid":"56781123677b9692bc8a15a26e2234d649dfa455","tid":335750,"uid":80426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"因為前輪轉向，後入會易控制對位"},{"pid":"73fe8fefc2e82c77d38cde3426739f5c4ed0dc1b","tid":335750,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"因為攞車果時型啲"},{"pid":"6658008355dedf6a1ea8b05e14e75f789c41a327","tid":335750,"uid":111343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:00:55.000Z","msg":"用個車頭入 退後出黎果時會轉向不足 因為你係用個頭轆控制方向<br />\n<br />\n用個車頭入係你退後出黎果時 只係用到後鏡 左右兩邊根本無辦法睇到 咁試問你點知有無車過緊黎"},{"pid":"f7a9646c00e6ad45489bb64a68a39f2f4d81522f","tid":335750,"uid":59948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:22:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主要係後泊有後泊鏡 預位準好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴撚線咩答案黎"},{"pid":"dfc381a813c498731369fd76719b3a1becad4c05","tid":335750,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>車頭入 架車唔會好直  除非直路到尾去泊車</blockquote><br />\n隊咗入去都已經冇位拉直架車<br />\n除非係劃斜位。不過斜位入，就會小咗一個車位。<br />\n一排小一個車位。成個成車停有幾十排。"},{"pid":"4c6a6bc7dce66c427cf203a06979652ab06e7b20","tid":335750,"uid":26353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"生轆前死轆後<br />\n冇車牌嘅你去百佳拎架手推車玩下啦<br />\n咁嘅嘢都要問"},{"pid":"6bbcdaf13075afdb3d42749e814ce0e4e35c461a","tid":335750,"uid":73123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:09:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生轆前死轆後<br />\n冇車牌嘅你去百佳拎架手推車玩下啦<br />\n咁嘅嘢都要問</blockquote><br />\n乜超市個d唔係四輪轉向咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d80fac2ccd8f822410adf5c4aa45cd96335c27","tid":335750,"uid":26353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:34:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生轆前死轆後<br />\n冇車牌嘅你去百佳拎架手推車玩下啦<br />\n咁嘅嘢都要問</blockquote><br />\n乜超市個d唔係四輪轉向咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大鐵籠嗰款你有冇見過"},{"pid":"9772b67cc09f8bb985e93740cc266db7aaff5066","tid":335750,"uid":73123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生轆前死轆後<br />\n冇車牌嘅你去百佳拎架手推車玩下啦<br />\n咁嘅嘢都要問</blockquote><br />\n乜超市個d唔係四輪轉向咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大鐵籠嗰款你有冇見過</blockquote><br />\n我諗我見識小，無印像見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae4f4f80caf622cfeaa58db7fb6edb333ba655f","tid":335750,"uid":13416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"泊一百次車可能有幾次係頭入<br />\n平時慣左尾入開車D波就走<br />\n試過有一次頭入開車果時唔撚記得左係用頭入....<br />\n最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d64786172c6800e14e9c2de07fd054d1c9d314","tid":335750,"uid":59466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>主要係後泊有後泊鏡 預位準好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴撚線咩答案黎</blockquote><br />\n諗到先好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb759d79cb02e26413c690ddde88955bac14be1","tid":335750,"uid":70510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:41:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解大部分泊車都係要倒車泊入去？<br />\n車頭泊入去倒車抽返出黎唔係應該易過倒車泊入去咩？</blockquote><br />\n如果你係外國<br />\n你會見到多數人用頭就咁扭入去<br />\n因為人地國家地大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以外國停車場意外率特別高, 當中大部份都係因為尾出時發生, 係外國住得耐就明, 得別多 on9 望都唔望直接倒出黎, 所以就算地方大如果能夠習慣尾入點都係好事"},{"pid":"4666fe2084b803445ba46b7d4348a1d7103a0f89","tid":335750,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T00:47:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解大部分泊車都係要倒車泊入去？<br />\n車頭泊入去倒車抽返出黎唔係應該易過倒車泊入去咩？</blockquote><br />\n如果你係外國<br />\n你會見到多數人用頭就咁扭入去<br />\n因為人地國家地大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以外國停車場意外率特別高, 當中大部份都係因為尾出時發生, 係外國住得耐就明, 得別多 on9 望都唔望直接倒出黎, 所以就算地方大如果能夠習慣尾入點都係好事</blockquote><br />\n鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e39dbfbf98229ba54d550fe07a862464d7fb7e","tid":335750,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"因為香港嘅停車場多數唔夠位俾車好方便地用頭入<br />\n頭入嗰下可能易，尾出嗰下難"}]}